 wandering all over trying to find the trigger point. Sure enough, the Death Squad appeared with 4 spawns.  But they didn't attack him because he's an ogre with acceptable faction!  After a minute or two, the Death Squad just despawned. Fifteen minutes later, we tried it again and Tanik triggered. I ran down, handed him the vial, and we were done.  Piece of cake.<br>
<br>
Now my buddy has this level 1 ogre who can run up and down a large part of Kael without being touched.  When he runs out of food, he just attacks a giant and respawns at his Kael bind point with newbie food and water.  Can you say infinite corpse retriever?<br>
<br>
Carazar Planeseeker<br>
