<br>
Don't forget to invis your Ogre if you send him into Kael for your corpse. The giants'll smoosh him if they see him dragging any corpse but his own. Of course, you don't lose anything but time when he dies, so if you're lying next to a See Invis giant send him in and drag yourself a few feet each pop.<br>
<br>
