<br>
I had previously trekked to Thurgadin with a level 10 Enchanter, but he had his own Invis and Gate. This level one business is pretty fun! I got him an Invis and a port to Iceclad, and a second Invis at the bridge to EW. He appeared about halfway across EW, but still made it to Kael unscathed. I must say I was sweating a litte even though I didn't stand to lose much.<br>
<br>
One word of warning: don't get cocky and attack Snow Bunnies. They hit HARD, and /con yellow at level one.<br>
<br>
Also, you know that Kromrif Recruiter guy right inside Kael that's completely immunt to magic and is a real bear to melee from what I hear? He /cons even to me at level one ;) <p>Zwobu &lt;Trade Foundation&gt; Innoruuk</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugherad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gherad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 86<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/4/01 3:35 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Duties of the Crown Quest</span><hr size=1> Hehe, he is level 1?  That guy has 1800 hps.  That has got to be the toughest level 1 mob in the game.  I have to use lures to take him out - he cannot move from his spot and is immune to most magic. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umcdermit.showPublicProfile?language=EN>mcdermit</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 177<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/4/01 3:41 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Duties of the Crown Quest</span><hr size=1> I snuck in there with my Wizard and laid down an Enticement of Flame, which he resisted. Do you need to be in melee range for this guy, or is fire the wrong flavor to use? Or was I just unlucky? <p>Zwobu &lt;Trade Foundation&gt; Innoruuk</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugherad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gherad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 87<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/4/01 5:47 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Duties o