I'm still finishing up part 3 of this quest (3 snow griffon eggs to go...).  However, while scouting around for Snow Griffons, I stumbled upon Tanik.  I had only glanced at the part 4 spoiler, and I wasn't very close to the Kael entrance, so I wasn't thinking about the Death Squad.  Here's what's interesting: I got a completely different dialog with him than what's reported here.<br>
<br>
He still said he needed a vial to save him, but he made no mention of it being a vial of Velium Vapors - when I asked what vial? he told me to kill some named being and give him the vial from his body.  About 15 seconds into me digesting this, the Death Squad spawned right on top of the FD'd dwarf, and among the death squad was this named Frost Giant he talked about.<br>
<br>
This happened on the 16th (yesterday, just before today's patch).  Is it possible this quest has been changed since last update here?  I didn't get a log, but if I see him again I'll turn logging on before I approach and hail him.<br>
